articles.title: 10 breathtaking photos of Supermoon 2024 - The Times of India
articles.description: ​A Supermoon occurs when the Moon is closest to Earth in its orbit, making it appear larger and brighter. In 2024, this celestial event displayed breathtaking views, illuminating skies with its extraordinary glow. Here are some marvellous pictures of the moon
